 Gabriel heard as another bot other than Kit Kat answered. His spark sank. He 
had never seen Kit Kat but her voice was a recorded historical moument in the 
capital city. It declared her battle cry the day they destroyed the 
alliance..."May our paths lead where they may" It was a common tone to him. 
He sent a comm back to the bot.."I am sorry but i must speak to her. She has 
to see what the furture holds. Or what it might not."
